disable combine_min_nan_groups check
combine_min_nan_groups is set to True by default but not min_group_size
leading to an exception
maybe change combine_min_nan_groups to False by default in the future?

Add logic to _transform_count_encode
needed for _handle_unknown == 'value' not to interfere with _handle_unknown =
'return_nan'

FAILED test_encoders.py::TestEncoders::test_handle_missing_return_nan_train - AssertionError: False is not true

set default for min_group_size
min_group_size is set to 0.01, setting of some value required for combine_min_nan.
